# =========================================
# Task API Tests (Protected)
# =========================================

### Create Task
POST http://localhost:5000/api/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Finish Primetrade Assignment",
  "description": "Complete frontend and backend integration"
}

### Get All Tasks
GET http://localhost:5000/api/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Task
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/tasks/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Finish Primetrade Assignment (Updated)",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "status": "completed"
}

### Delete Task
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/tasks/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
